m is the key this time. He is unbeaten on a heavy track, and a big run would not surprise.\",\"runners\":[7,3,4,2,14],\"exclusive\":true}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"NZ TAB","tipRunnerNumbers":[1,3,10,2]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[7,10,6,9]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,8,7,5]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[9,4,2,12]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,5,3,6]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,6,1,9]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,7,1,12]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,7,5,3]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"RunningDouble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quaddie","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Treble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}}]}}}